name: The Lighthouse #2
description:
Second image of the "Lighthouse Collection". The entire "Lighthouse Collection" use the same photograph as a base, which can be found on mi ig and soon as nft in H=N. All the images of the collection are generated by CLIP guided diffusion and edited in photoshop. There will be 20 unique lighthouses in the collection.

The "Lighthouse Collection" is intended to be the first collection of a project that explores the ai generated art mixed with photos.
